64
00:03:11,943 --> 00:03:13,943
Sincronia: sid, PeSoberbo, FláP,
Brubzinha, gugasms e Tarcisio.

65
00:03:13,944 --> 00:03:15,944
Revisão: Smooth,
JuhSuedde e FláP

66
